                intervention.
              </p>
            </>
          ))
          .with('en', () => (
            <>
              <h2>How does Project Boost work?</h2>
              <p>
                Our engagement unfolds in several phases to ensure effective
                integration and fast results.
              </p>
              <h3>1. Immersion and onboarding</h3>
              <p>
